(1)Division of Clinical Epidemiology and Aging Research, German Cancer Research 
Center, Heidelberg, Germany. e.raum@dkfz-heidelberg.de

BACKGROUND: To examine lifetime patterns of cardiovascular risk factors and 
their implications in subsequent birth cohorts of older adults in Germany, who 
experienced very different political and socioeconomic conditions at various 
