Bernhard J(1), Zahrieh D, Zhang JJ, Martinelli G, Basser R, Hürny C, Forbes JF, 
Aebi S, Yeo W, Thürlimann B, Green MD, Colleoni M, Gelber RD, 
Castiglione-Gertsch M, Price KN, Goldhirsch A, Coates AS; International Breast 
